transcript.text: Hello, welcome to on print shop.

In this video we will see the upload center proof tool enhancement earlier for any product if upload center proof is set as designer studio from product settings tab, if we select any size for a product from storefront and click on upload center and upload a file and click on checkout button, we land in designer studio.
But orientation of the canvas depends on orientation of size only.
In version 7.1 we have enhanced logic of loading studio canvas orientation.
Now based on the orientation of image uploaded from upload center flow studios canvas will get oriented.
That is if initially canvas is in portrait mode but uploaded image file is in landscape then the canvas will automatically load in landscape mode.
Also in the upload proofing tool, we have added a rotate design feature.
This will for sure help your customers to proof their design and make the desired changes with more ease.
We also introduced canvas orientation button.
We can click on this button to change the orientation of the canvas according to our requirements.
Thank you for watching this video.
For more help, please send us an e-mail at support at on printshop.com.
